  <p class="content"><p>"People especially interested in a pot they don't have to stir might not be the most helpful when it comes to getting up and donating to a young project."</p>
<p>Nah, see, I'm pretty sure this is the kind of project that might actually do particularly well on Kickstarter: it's a simple idea that just needs money, and so long as he can come up with a couple of good backer bonuses, he should be sorted.</p>
